本研究藉由超國界法律所提供的一個視野，以及聯結國際法與國內法的關係，再用於實現個案正義，由於兩岸特殊之政治問題、歷史背景，究竟從大陸地區遠嫁台灣地區的配偶，在未取得身份證之前，在台灣生活將會遇到怎麼樣的問題？而我們的法律又是如何規定的？是否有異於其他國家的婚姻移民呢？而我們的法律規範，若從超國界法律思維來看，是否能與國際普世人權價值相容。本研究希冀從超國界法律觀點，重新作案例的討論，並分析兩岸人民關係條例等法規範，對於兩岸婚姻移民不論政策面、法制面、執行面之問題，期望能跳脫原來思考的疆界與藩籬，進而保障兩岸人民之基本人權。

This research by  Trasnational law provide of a visual field, and combine the international law relationship with domestic method, be used for again to carry out individual case justice, marry the spouse of Taiwanese region far from mainland region actually due to the cross-straits special political issue, history background, will meet in the Taiwanese life before doing not obtain ID card how of problem?And our law again is how rule?Whether differ with the marriage of other nations emigrant?And our laws standard, if from the super national boundary law thinking to see, whether ability and international Pu people of this world power value compatible.This research craves for standpoint from the Trasnational law , re- committing crime the discussion of example, and analyzing cross-straits people to relate to regulation etc. method standard, immigrate a policy to face in spite of to the cross-straits marriage, the legal system face, the problem of performance, expect Jiang boundary and barrier that can jump to take off to consider originally, then guarantee the cross-straits people''s basic human rights.

